name: Doge Run
description: DogeRun is a Play to Earn game that incorporates the addictiveness of a run themed game while giving investors a chance to earn attractive profits. It is based off timeless classic's such as mario run and geometry dash. Level one is fully playable at launch with the Play to Earn features and NFT collection coming soon The goal of the game is to finish the level as quickly as possible while collecting coins and powerups while avoiding obstacles and enemies.
